  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into a dystopian adventure crafted for those who appreciate powerfully brief experiences. <strong>Full Void</strong> will give you a gripping story set in a future where AI has gained control of humanity. As a lone teenager, with only your hacking skills at your disposal, you'll navigate a haunting, abandoned world brought to life through stunning handcrafted pixel art. Designed as a short yet unforgettable journey, this cinematic puzzle-platformer is perfect even for a single sitting, leaving a lasting impression with its retro aesthetics and emotional depth. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/cd48762d804cd2f64906f964b5fb9ee5.poster.avif?t=1734096524\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/cd48762d804cd2f64906f964b5fb9ee5.webm?t=1734096524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Hack your way through a deadly environment where every step could be your last. Will you run from lethal enemies or try to control them? Use your skills to fight, solve puzzles and find a way to fix this crumbling society, where only children are still free. But for how long?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/f24f0f6e7755dfe353bc890acc7d069b.poster.avif?t=1734096524\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/f24f0f6e7755dfe353bc890acc7d069b.webm?t=1734096524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Dive into a dark world where a rogue AI holds humanity in a comforting yet insidious grip. You play as a young teenager still free in this hostile, dystopian future. Although scared and alone, you will have to keep going to discover the truth around this broken society.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/d55a25bfd96e6e2c850b569238766d84.poster.avif?t=1734096524\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/d55a25bfd96e6e2c850b569238766d84.webm?t=1734096524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Leap across a hand crafted retro-style world, through abandoned cities to eerie labs. Brave each jump, face the unknown. Full Void is a spiritual successor to classic cinematic puzzle platformers such as Prince of Persia, Another World (Out of This World) and Flashback, with a modern twist, innovative visuals and gameplay mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/a6dff0684284e18eb2fb700e40b93c0b.apng?t=1734096524\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/a6dff0684284e18eb2fb700e40b93c0b.poster.avif?t=1734096524\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=180 /></picture></span>Step into Full Void's 16-bit pixel world, where retro aesthetics blend with modern elements. Experience a new classic that encapsulates nostalgic vibes while offering fresh, engaging visuals and gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/e4d4d5dc70f591d3bea648e4a86b115a.poster.avif?t=1734096524\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/e4d4d5dc70f591d3bea648e4a86b115a.webm?t=1734096524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Immerse yourself in Full Void's ambient sounds, setting a tense, horror ambiance without the gore. With our original Amiga MOD music taking the center stage, relish a nod to classic gaming as it enhances every suspense-filled moment in your voyage through a dystopian reality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/e33cde2991b91e0ee48fcfe74dd8c4a8.avif?t=1734096524\" width=600 height=92 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/9983b2fe893e6645236957c879f12f77.avif?t=1734096524\" width=600 height=347 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into a dystopian adventure crafted for those who appreciate powerfully brief experiences. <strong>Full Void</strong> will give you a gripping story set in a future where AI has gained control of humanity. As a lone teenager, with only your hacking skills at your disposal, you'll navigate a haunting, abandoned world brought to life through stunning handcrafted pixel art. Designed as a short yet unforgettable journey, this cinematic puzzle-platformer is perfect even for a single sitting, leaving a lasting impression with its retro aesthetics and emotional depth. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/cd48762d804cd2f64906f964b5fb9ee5.poster.avif?t=1734096524\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/cd48762d804cd2f64906f964b5fb9ee5.webm?t=1734096524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Hack your way through a deadly environment where every step could be your last. Will you run from lethal enemies or try to control them? Use your skills to fight, solve puzzles and find a way to fix this crumbling society, where only children are still free. But for how long?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/f24f0f6e7755dfe353bc890acc7d069b.poster.avif?t=1734096524\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/f24f0f6e7755dfe353bc890acc7d069b.webm?t=1734096524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Dive into a dark world where a rogue AI holds humanity in a comforting yet insidious grip. You play as a young teenager still free in this hostile, dystopian future. Although scared and alone, you will have to keep going to discover the truth around this broken society.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/d55a25bfd96e6e2c850b569238766d84.poster.avif?t=1734096524\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/d55a25bfd96e6e2c850b569238766d84.webm?t=1734096524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Leap across a hand crafted retro-style world, through abandoned cities to eerie labs. Brave each jump, face the unknown. Full Void is a spiritual successor to classic cinematic puzzle platformers such as Prince of Persia, Another World (Out of This World) and Flashback, with a modern twist, innovative visuals and gameplay mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/a6dff0684284e18eb2fb700e40b93c0b.apng?t=1734096524\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/a6dff0684284e18eb2fb700e40b93c0b.poster.avif?t=1734096524\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=180 /></picture></span>Step into Full Void's 16-bit pixel world, where retro aesthetics blend with modern elements. Experience a new classic that encapsulates nostalgic vibes while offering fresh, engaging visuals and gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/e4d4d5dc70f591d3bea648e4a86b115a.poster.avif?t=1734096524\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/e4d4d5dc70f591d3bea648e4a86b115a.webm?t=1734096524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Immerse yourself in Full Void's ambient sounds, setting a tense, horror ambiance without the gore. With our original Amiga MOD music taking the center stage, relish a nod to classic gaming as it enhances every suspense-filled moment in your voyage through a dystopian reality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/e33cde2991b91e0ee48fcfe74dd8c4a8.avif?t=1734096524\" width=600 height=92 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/9983b2fe893e6645236957c879f12f77.avif?t=1734096524\" width=600 height=347 /></span></p>",
